    "poem": "In Aalborg, clouds will gently play, \nwith 8.7 degrees, a gentle day.\nBut Frederikshavn's winds will boldly blow, \nand Hanstholm's clouds will part to let you go.\nThe birthplace is chill, with humidity high, \nbut which is best for moose hunting, I wonder why?\n\nI Danmark, Aalborg er mest behagelig, \nmed lav vind og ingen regn, best for moose hunting, \nfor selv elgen ville vælge dette sted, \nfor at gemme sig, med en god chance for at blive set, \nså tag dine våben, og vær parat, \nfor moose hunting i Aalborg, hvor elgen vil sagtne!",
